---
title: Smoky Chipotle Chicken Sandos with Mini Potato Coins
description: Tender chicken thighs coated in Southwest spices and slathered with smoky chipotle sauce will have you screaming with delight! But don't fret — our chipotle sauce is more smoky than spicy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-de-poulet-fume-au-chipotle-72a75b2d.jpg
